  "None suggested yet": "Ingen forslag endnu",
  "After the AI responds, a separate quiet API call generates the tracker JSON independently. Expect ~250–300s total per message (narrative + wait + tracker).": "Efter svaret genererer et stille kald JSON. ~250–300s/besked.",
