  "✓ 2–3× faster than Separate mode in practice": "✓ 2–3× hurtigere end Separat",
  "✗ Uses tokens from the main response budget (~1,700 tokens for tracker)": "✗ Bruger tokens fra hovedbudgettet (~1.700)",
