  "✗ Embeds previous snapshot into narrative call (~1.9K tokens) unless Embed snapshots = 0": "✗ Indlejrer snapshot (~1.9K) medmindre = 0",
  "How many recent messages to include when generating tracker updates.": "Hvor mange seneste beskeder.",
  "Separate mode only — Together mode uses ST's full context automatically.": "Kun Separat — Sammen bruger STs kontekst.",
  "Fastest. Good for simple 1-on-1 scenes (~5K token prompt)": "Hurtigste. For 1-mod-1-scener (~5K)",
