  "Maximum context but significantly slower and more expensive": "Maksimal kontekst men langsommere og dyrere",
  "This is the biggest factor in Separate mode speed. At 8 msgs your tracker prompt is ~10K tokens — doubling roughly doubles generation time. Lower values (3–4) can cut tracker time by 40–60%.": "Største faktor. 8 beskeder ~10K — fordobling fordobler. 3–4 reducerer 40–60%.",
  "Separate mode only.": "Kun Separat tilstand.",
  "How many times to retry if the tracker API call returns invalid JSON.": "Antal genforsøg ved ugyldig JSON.",
  "Built-in preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Optimized for structured JSON output on GLM-5.": "Preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Til JSON på GLM-5.",
  "Embed recent scene snapshots into the narrative conversation context so the AI can reference tracker state while writing. Only applies in Separate mode. The tracker's own API call always receives the previous snapshot regardless of this setting.": "Indlejrer snapshots i konteksten. Kun Separat. Trackeren modtager altid den forrige.",
  "Each embedded snapshot adds ~1.9K tokens to your narrative prompt. Set to 0 to eliminate this overhead — the tracker API call still receives previous state independently. Set to 1 for narrative continuity (AI remembers scene details). Values above 1 are rarely beneficial.": "Hvert snapshot +~1.9K. 0 fjerner. 1 for kontinuitet. Over 1 sjældent nyttigt.",
  "Injected as invisible context — AI treats it as authoritative background info. Best for continuity without polluting the conversation.": "Indsprøjtet som usynlig kontekst — autoritativ baggrund.",
